snippet.textDisplay: Thank you Coke Studio for making it happen - We humbly thanks to all the musicians who infused soul in the song, Omran Shafique Haniya Aslam Mannu, Fakir Zulfiqar, Bhagat Bhooro Laal, Kami Paul Rufus Shahzad, Babar Khanna & Zohaib Kazi Ali Hamza for allowing us to create with freedom. Humbled thanks for fans and listeners who are listening to us first time or have been listening our music 🙏🏽🙏🏽 - This Story is very close to my heart and interesting village of Rano (Amarkot, Sindhi) is now in the part of Pakistani side of Tharr & Village of Moomal is now in India part of Rajhistan (Gajmail or Jesalmir) which was once one land. I hope people Tharr or Rajhistan will enjoy their lore as well as everyone else 😊❤️ - The story is written in the poetry of Sindhi Poet 'Shah Latif Bhittai as a sacred story as sacred as Bhittai. I have always been in Love with the Moomal of Kaak as Bhittai expressed her and grew up imagining her and We're so happy that we chose to sing this Lore. Love ❤️
snippet.textOriginal: Thank you Coke Studio for making it happen - We humbly thanks to all the musicians who infused soul in the song, Omran Shafique Haniya Aslam Mannu, Fakir Zulfiqar, Bhagat Bhooro Laal, Kami Paul Rufus Shahzad, Babar Khanna & Zohaib Kazi Ali Hamza for allowing us to create with freedom. Humbled thanks for fans and listeners who are listening to us first time or have been listening our music 🙏🏽🙏🏽 - This Story is very close to my heart and interesting village of Rano (Amarkot, Sindhi) is now in the part of Pakistani side of Tharr & Village of Moomal is now in India part of Rajhistan (Gajmail or Jesalmir) which was once one land. I hope people Tharr or Rajhistan will enjoy their lore as well as everyone else 😊❤️ - The story is written in the poetry of Sindhi Poet 'Shah Latif Bhittai as a sacred story as sacred as Bhittai. I have always been in Love with the Moomal of Kaak as Bhittai expressed her and grew up imagining her and We're so happy that we chose to sing this Lore. Love ❤️
